metadata.name: Space Doodles
metadata.description:
Space Doodles are spaceships for your Doodle. Each Doodle in the original collection of 10,000 can launch their own personal spaceship that is generated from over 200 audio-visual traits and on-chain stats.

Your Space Doodle is your Doodle and selling it will allow the new purchaser to remove the Doodle from our secure smart contract.
